## Third-Party Data and Services

This software uses data and services from third-party providers. Users must
comply with the respective terms and licenses of these providers:

### Satellite Data
- **EUMETSAT**: Data provided by the European Organisation for the Exploitation
  of Meteorological Satellites. Subject to EUMETSAT data policy and terms of use.
  - GeoColour RGB - MTG: https://data.eumetsat.int/product/EO:EUM:DAT:0913
  - Fog / Low Clouds RGB - MTG-I: https://data.eumetsat.int/product/EO:EUM:DAT:1023

- **NASA GIBS**: Data provided by NASA's Global Imagery Browse Services.
  Subject to NASA data policy and terms of use.
  - NOAA-2 / VIIRS: https://www.earthdata.nasa.gov/data/catalog/lancemodis-vj103mod-nrt-2.1

### Geographic Data
- **Natural Earth Data**: Public domain map data
  - Source: https://www.naturalearthdata.com/
  - License: Public Domain
  - Terms: https://www.naturalearthdata.com/about/terms-of-use/

- **OpenStreetMap**: Open data licensed under ODbL
  - Source: https://www.openstreetmap.org/
  - License: Open Database License (ODbL)
  - Terms: https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright

### Basemaps
- **Esri World Imagery**: Provided by Esri
  - Source: https://www.esri.com/
  - Subject to Esri Terms of Use

### Libraries
- **Leaflet.js**: Open-source JavaScript library for interactive maps
  - Source: https://leafletjs.com/
  - License: BSD 2-Clause License
  - Copyright (c) 2010-2023, Vladimir Agafonkin
  - Copyright (c) 2010-2023, CloudMade

